{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-hackers-js","path":"/hackers/following.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Hacker Following enables you to to keep up-to-date with your favorite hackers as you can see their activity on HackerOne.</p>\n<p>To follow a hacker:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to the hacker’s profile page.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Follow</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 400px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 138.39999999999998%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"follow button on hacker profile\"\n        title=\"follow button on hacker profile\"\n        src=\"/static/026f4220095f83b5508347241c414480/e17e5/following-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/026f4220095f83b5508347241c414480/fac75/following-1.png 125w,\n/static/026f4220095f83b5508347241c414480/63868/following-1.png 250w,\n/static/026f4220095f83b5508347241c414480/e17e5/following-1.png 400w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><em>Follow</em> will change to <em>Following</em> to denote that you’re following the hacker.</p>\n<h3 id=\"filtering-out-followers\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#filtering-out-followers\" aria-label=\"filtering out followers permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Filtering out Followers</h3>\n<p>To solely view the activity of the hackers you’re following on Hacktivity, select the <strong>Hackers I am following</strong> filter.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 306px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 39.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Hackers I am following filter\"\n        title=\"Hackers I am following filter\"\n        src=\"/static/a30a929fad22a38138ebbdb87d394479/98b92/following-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a30a929fad22a38138ebbdb87d394479/fac75/following-2.png 125w,\n/static/a30a929fad22a38138ebbdb87d394479/63868/following-2.png 250w,\n/static/a30a929fad22a38138ebbdb87d394479/98b92/following-2.png 306w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 306px) 100vw, 306px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"managing-followed-hackers\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#managing-followed-hackers\" aria-label=\"managing followed hackers permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Managing Followed Hackers</h3>\n<p>To manage all of the hackers you’re following:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to Hacker Dashboard > Followed Hackers.</li>\n<li><em>(Optional)</em> Click <strong>Unfollow</strong> to stop following any hackers you no longer wish to keep track of.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 24.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"followed hackers page\"\n        title=\"followed hackers page\"\n        src=\"/static/abba12164fa0e3101b6e4d57f7c58c17/0b533/following-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/abba12164fa0e3101b6e4d57f7c58c17/fac75/following-3.png 125w,\n/static/abba12164fa0e3101b6e4d57f7c58c17/63868/following-3.png 250w,\n/static/abba12164fa0e3101b6e4d57f7c58c17/0b533/following-3.png 500w,\n/static/abba12164fa0e3101b6e4d57f7c58c17/1d69c/following-3.png 750w,\n/static/abba12164fa0e3101b6e4d57f7c58c17/00d43/following-3.png 1000w,\n/static/abba12164fa0e3101b6e4d57f7c58c17/93ba6/following-3.png 2874w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Hacker Following","id":"hackers/following","path":"/hackers/following.html","description":null},"headings":[{"value":"Filtering out Followers"},{"value":"Managing Followed Hackers"}]}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}